      <title>“挫败感和疲劳”击中了股票交易者的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/exasperated-stock-traders-are-flying-blind-in-this-tariff-storm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府关于周三将揭幕哪些新关税的混合消息，以及他们将如何宣布他们的股票交易者在试图围绕多年来面临的最大风险的位置时感到震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/exasperated-stock-traders-are-flying-blind-in-this-tariff-storm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 16:04:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IDC援助涉及南非钢铁钢米尔的固定链接</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/idc-aid-staves-off-arcelormittal-south-africa-steel-mill-closure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当地国家发展机构同意提供16.83亿兰德（9100万美元）的设施后，Arcelormittal SA的南非单位将在六个月内推迟计划关闭两个钢铁厂的关闭，并承诺解决困扰该行业的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/idc-aid-staves-off-arcelormittal-south-africa-steel-mill-closure</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 16:03:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Allianz全球投资者抛弃某些ESG资金的武器禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/allianz-global-investors-to-drop-weapons-ban-for-some-esg-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安联全球投资者将允许以前被禁止的与国防相关的资产在某些ESG基金中持有，此举说，这一举动反映了欧洲的新地缘政治现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/allianz-global-investors-to-drop-weapons-ban-for-some-esg-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 16:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
