    <item>
      <title>欧洲股票随着关税威胁凹痕强季度下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/european-stocks-fall-as-tariff-threat-dents-strong-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股票连续第四天下跌，因为进一步的美国关税袭击了最容易受到贸易紧张局势的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/european-stocks-fall-as-tariff-threat-dents-strong-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 07:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿斯顿·马丁（Aston Martin）的漫步说，他愿意私下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/aston-martin-to-raise-125-million-by-selling-shares-f1-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯顿·马丁·拉贡达（Aston Martin Lagonda）全球控股公司（Aston Martin Lagonda Boldings Plc）的执行董事长劳伦斯·斯特罗尔（Lawrence Stroll）表示，在宣布注入更多资金的计划之后，他将来将愿意将这家豪华汽车制造商私有化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/aston-martin-to-raise-125-million-by-selling-shares-f1-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 06:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场股票随着美国关税的担忧而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/emerging-currencies-steady-after-china-data-with-us-tariffs-eyed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者急切地离开唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的全球关税计划，新兴市场的股票连续第三天暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/emerging-currencies-steady-after-china-data-with-us-tariffs-eyed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 04:03:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当交易者权衡特朗普对俄罗斯原油的威胁时，石油的进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）建议美国可能努力减少俄罗斯的原油运输之后，石油上升了，俄罗斯是世界第三大生产商和主要出口商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 23:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500装饰掉落，因为关税摇摆不定地球：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/us-stock-futures-tumble-ahead-of-new-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税推广前几天，一阵新的波动率袭击了全球市场，对经济放缓驱动股票的担忧加剧了，因为交易者急于兑现债券和黄金的安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/us-stock-futures-tumble-ahead-of-new-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 22:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人群群特斯拉陈列室在全国范围内抗议Elon Musk</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-29/protesters-rebelling-against-elon-musk-s-purge-of-us-government-swarm-tesla-showrooms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山（AP）＆Mdash;抗议者反对亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）在总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）领导下对美国政府的清除，在周六的特斯拉经销店和欧洲一些城市外展示了最新的尝试，以削弱世界上最富有的人的财富。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-29/protesters-rebelling-against-elon-musk-s-purge-of-us-government-swarm-tesla-showrooms</guid>
